    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@seafoox following your proposal, I submitted #765 which change:\n- social github button\n- lower down big white blank space by adding more text\n- use font-weight normal on widget names in doc\n- low contrast on code in white background areas\n- various text fixes formatting that we missed or introduced recently\n\nAlso anchors were already done in the doc webpage.\n\nThere's an issue for bower already #351 \n\nAnd as for the links on the homepage I think we are good as we want people to really scroll and get the effect\n\nThanks a lot for the feedback and sorry for the verrrrrrrrrrry late reply.\n",
